content: I think #13556 (ci: report changes to the import graph in a spoiler comment) has broken CI for any PR based on a mathlib version including that PR. I'm seeing error: pathspec 'origin/import-count' did not match any file(s) known to git in an unrelated new PR (#13580).
Try again. Should work now. We definitely need the "follow up PR" mentioned in #13556
